Q: Compute $\tan \left( \arccos \frac{1}{3} \right).$

solution:
Consider a right triangle where the adjacent side is 1 and the hypotenuse is 3.

[asy]
unitsize (1 cm);

draw((0,0)--(1,0)--(1,2*sqrt(2))--cycle);

